<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Update - {{orderNumber}}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2D5CFF 0%, #1E40AF 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        
        .status-update {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f2fd 0%, #f3e5f5 100%);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border: 1px solid #e1bee7;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .status-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: block;
        }
        
        .status-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .status-message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .badge-processing { background-color: #2196f3; color: white; }
        .badge-shipped { background-color: #ff9800; color: white; }
        .badge-delivered { background-color: #4caf50; color: white; }
        .badge-cancelled { background-color: #f44336; color: white; }
        
        .order-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .info-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #666;
            min-width: 140px;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-align: right;
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .tracking-number {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .delivery-estimate {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4caf50;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .delivery-estimate h4 {
            color: #2e7d32;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .delivery-estimate p {
            color: #388e3c;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2D5CFF 0%, #1E40AF 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #2D5CFF;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .help-section {
            background-color: #fff8e1;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .help-section h4 {
            color: #f57f17;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .help-section p {
            color: #f57f17;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 0 10px;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .info-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
            
            .info-value {
                text-align: left;
                margin-top: 4px;
            }
            
            .status-update {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Order Update üì¶</h1>
            <p>Your order status has been updated</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <!-- Status Update Section -->
            <div class="status-update">
                <div class="status-icon">{{statusIcon}}</div>
                <div class="status-title">{{statusTitle}}</div>
                <div class="status-message">{{statusMessage}}</div>
                <span class="status-badge badge-{{statusClass}}">{{status}}</span>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Order Information -->
            <div class="order-info">
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Order Number:</span>
                    <span class="info-value"><strong>{{orderNumber}}</strong></span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Tracking Number:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">
                        <span class="tracking-number">{{trackingNumber}}</span>
                    </span>
                </div>
                {{#if orderDate}}
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Order Date:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{orderDate}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Last Updated:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{lastUpdated}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Delivery Estimate (if available) -->
            {{#if estimatedDelivery}}
            <div class="delivery-estimate">
                <h4>üì¶ Estimated Delivery</h4>
                <p><strong>{{estimatedDelivery}}</strong></p>
                <p style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: 14px;">We'll notify you when your order is out for delivery</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <!-- Call to Action -->
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{trackingUrl}}" class="cta-button">View Order Details</a>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Help Section -->
            <div class="help-section">
                <h4>Need Help? ü§ù</h4>
                <p><strong>Questions about your order?</strong> Contact our support team</p>
                <p>üìß Email: <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #f57f17;">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
                <p>üïí We typically respond within 2-4 hours during business hours</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Status-specific Information -->
            {{#if (eq statusClass "processing")}}
            <div style="background-color: #e3f2fd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;">
                <h4 style="color: #1976d2; margin-bottom: 8px;">‚è≥ What's happening now?</h4>
                <p style="color: #1976d2; font-size: 14px;">
                    Your order is being carefully prepared and will be shipped within 1-2 business days.
                </p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if (eq statusClass "shipped")}}
            <div style="background-color: #fff3e0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;">
                <h4 style="color: #f57c00; margin-bottom: 8px;">üöö Your order is on the way!</h4>
                <p style="color: #f57c00; font-size: 14px;">
                    Your package is now with our delivery partner and heading to your address.
                </p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if (eq statusClass "delivered")}}
            <div style="background-color: #e8f5e8; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #4caf50;">
                <h4 style="color: #388e3c; margin-bottom: 8px;">üéâ Delivery Complete!</h4>
                <p style="color: #388e3c; font-size: 14px;">
                    Thank you for shopping with Bareloft! We hope you love your purchase.
                </p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Stay Updated</strong></p>
            <p>We'll continue to send you updates as your order progresses</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
                Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.8;">
                This email was sent to {{customerEmail}}. You received this because you have an active order with Bareloft.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.8;">
                ¬© 2024 Bareloft. Lagos, Nigeria.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>